    <mxCell id="title" value="BioBridge-GraphRAG 粗筛—精排两阶段方案推荐范式" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=16;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#1F2A36;" vertex="1" parent="1">
